title.rendered: Day 4 with a big success for the UK team

content.rendered: Victoria Farrant is the president of Rockdonnell. And it seems that, need verification, that two other of the UK team members are in high ranking positions and two of the EU team members are as well. I am sure that Victoria will be very busy as president but will fill us in with who was elected to what position later. From now on there will not be much time for shopping, swimming or sleep until Monday night.
